[Although the number of reported cases of _Vibrio cholerae_ infection has decreased to the point where Haiti is not number 1 in cases currently in 2014 (Nigeria and Ghana have more), this is the beginning of the 5th year of the outbreak without a real end in sight. - Mod.LL

